import React, { useEffect, useState } from 'react'; import axios from 'axios'; import { useParams } from 'react-router-dom'; const MyProfile = () => { const [user, setUser] = useState(null); const { id } = useParams(); useEffect(() => { axios.get(`http://localhost:8080/Profile/User/${id}`) .then(response => { setUser(response.data); }) .catch(error => { console.error('Error fetching User:', error); }); }, [id]); return (
